title: Sagittarius Celebration & Tribute Sat. Dec 12th @ Rocky's 34th St. NYC
desc: Join us for a great time with friends old & new as we celebrate the sign of Sagittarius (DJ Don Welch & Friends). We will also pay Tribute & Celebrate the greatest radio personality ever to grace the air waves "Chief Rocker Frankie "Hollywood" Crocker. At the beautiful Rocky's on 34th Street NYC where there will be dancing, a special live performance and tasty treats & hors d'oeuvres. Hosted by Elmo "The Magic" Christian, Bea Montgomery & Veronica Evans. Tell a friend & see you on the dance floor.
